    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! It absolutely breaks my heart to even think about parting with this beauty, but my loss is definitely your gain. I\u2019ve babied this car since day one\u2014it's been tucked away in a climate-controlled garage and I\u2019ve spent more weekends polishing it than I care to admit! It\u2019s essentially in the same stunning shape as the day it left the showroom. You won\u2019t find a single blemish, and it still has that wonderful 'new car' scent. It drives like an absolute dream, smooth and responsive. I'm only selling to make space for a new family project, so I\u2019m looking for a fellow enthusiast who will cherish it. Come on over, let's chat cars, and you can see for yourself why this is the one you've been waiting for!",
